        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Kali22-kilavi">itu pirivuṇarttappaṭṭa tōḻi ataṟku uṭampaṭātu talaimakaṉai neruṅkik 
            kaḷavukālattoḻukkam eṭuttukkāṭṭi āṟṟuvittu uṭampaṭṭa vāypāṭṭāṉ maṟuttatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante, who had been informed of the separation, without agreeing to that approached the hero [and] refused by an allusion that [seemed to] agree [but] encouraged [to stay] by bringing up [and] showing the conduct for the period of secrecy.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Kali22">
                <l>uṇkaṭaṉ vaḻimoḻin tirakkuṅkāṉ mukaṉuntāṅ</l>
                <l>koṇṭatu koṭukkuṅkāṉ mukaṉumvē ṟākutal</l>
                <l>paṇṭumiv vulakat tiyaṟkai yaḵtiṉṟum</l>
                <l>putuva taṉṟē pulaṉuṭai māntir</l>
                <l>tāyuyir peyta pāvai pōla</l>
                <l>nalaṉuṭai yārmoḻikkaṭ ṭāvārtān tannalan</l>
                <l>tātutēr paṟavaiyi ṉaruntiṟal koṭukkuṅkā</l>
                <l>lētilār kūṟuva tevaṉōniṉ poruḷvēṭkai;</l>
                <l rend="space">naṟumullai nērmukai yoppa niraitta</l>
                <l>ceṟimuṟai pārāṭṭi ṉāymaṟṟem palliṉ</l>
                <l>paṟimuṟai pārāṭ ṭiṉaiyō vaiya;</l>
                <l rend="space">neyyiṭai nīvi maṇiyoḷi viṭṭaṉṉa</l>
                <l>vaivakai pārāṭṭi ṉāymaṟṟeṅ kūntaṟ</l>
                <l>ceyviṉai pārāṭ ṭiṉaiyō vaiya;</l>
                <l rend="space">kuḷaṉaṇi tāmaraip pācarum pēykku</l>
                <l>miḷamulai pārāṭṭi ṉāymaṟṟem mārpiṟ</l>
                <l>ṟaḷarmulai pārāṭ ṭiṉaiyō vaiya;</l>
                <l rend="space">eṉavāṅku,</l>
                <l>aṭarpo ṉavirēykku mavvari vāṭac</l>
                <l>cuṭarkāy curampōku nummaiyā meṅkaṭ</l>
                <l>paṭarkūṟa niṉṟatu muṇṭō toṭarkūrat</l>
                <l>tuvvāmai vantak kaṭai.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>            That the face will be different at the time of begging, praising the duty</l>
<l corresp="1f">of eating, from the face at the time of giving what they take </l>
<l corresp="3">that is the nature of this world of old. Today too, </l>
<l corresp="4">that is nothing new, you men of wisdom. </l>
<l corresp="5">Similar to dolls into whom the mothers poured life </l>
<l corresp="6a-c">there are those who don’t perish on account of words that possess goodness. </l>
<l corresp="8">What would a stranger say of you desire for wealth </l>
<l corresp="6d-7">at the time it brings ruin when, like by a bee that searches pollen their beauty is eaten? </l>
<l rend="space">You praised our teeth for [their] tight order</l>
<l>that were lined up like fine buds of fragrant jasmine.</l>
<l>Would you [also] praise [their] crooked order, lord?</l>
<l rend="space">You praise our tresses for [their] five kinds</l>
<l>that were as if emitting sapphire light after rubbing oil in.</l>
<l>Would you [also] praise the work to be done, lord?</l>
<l rend="space">You praised our chest for [our] young breasts</l>
<l>that resemble the green buds of the day lotus that adorns the pond.</l>
<l>Would you [also] praise [our] slackening breasts, lord?</l>
<l rend="space">That is to say,</l>
<l rend="space">while that line fades that resembles the sheen of gold plates,</l>
<l>when we talk to you, who go to the glowing hot desert,</l>
<l>on our behalf, is there anything that will last</l>
<l>until [you] come [back], not enjoying while the link is strong? </l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
